item.title: About Me
item.description: Name: Ishan Nangia Current Occupation: Data Scientist at Locus.sh In My Free Time: Birding, Reading about Wildlife, Badminton, Trying out new food I am a confused person who tries to make sense of things around him but fails to do so repeatedly. Constantly trying to figure out where to go from where I am. Zero patience…
